                                    </div>
                                    <div class="problem-details" id="maxcut-details">
                                        <p>Partition graph vertices to maximize edges between partitions.</p>
                                        <div class="problem-specs">
                                            <span><strong>Complexity:</strong> NP-hard</span>
                                            <span><strong>Applications:</strong> Network design, VLSI layout</span>
                                            <span><strong>Qubits:</strong> n (one per vertex)</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="problem-item" onclick="toggleProblemDetails('tsp')">
                                    <div class="problem-header">
                                        <span class="problem-icon">✅</span>
                                        <span class="problem-name">Traveling Salesman (TSP)</span>
                                        <span class="problem-badge">Classic</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="problem-details" id="tsp-details">
                                        <p>Find the shortest route visiting all cities exactly once.</p>
