                                            <span><strong>Complexity:</strong> NP-hard</span>
                                            <span><strong>Applications:</strong> Logistics, routing</span>
                                            <span><strong>Qubits:</strong> n² (n cities)</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="problem-item" onclick="toggleProblemDetails('graphcolor')">
